@{_Section "Registration"}

@{LIndent 0}@{Line}
Please read @{u}carefully@{uu} the following text!@{par}


@{u}PalmGear H.Q. Registration@{uu}@{par}

You can register via PalmGear H.Q. by one of the following methods:@{par}

Phone: (817) 640-6558@{par}
Fax  : (817) 640-6614@{par}
Web  : @{"PalmGear H.Q." SYSTEM "OpenURL http://www.palmgear.com"}@{par}

The registration fee using PalmGear H.Q. is $25 US.  This higher cost is to offset the expenses in using an on-line service.@{par}


@{u}Direct Author Registration@{uu}@{par}

To register, please print the @{"registration form" link Registrationform}, neatly complete it and send it to me along with the required sum of money.@{par}

The registration fee is $20 US or $30 CND (Canadian dollars)@{par}
If you registered Spitfire before February, 2000, then the upgrade fee is $10 US or $15 CND (Canadian dollars)@{par}

You can choose between various methods of payment:@{LIndent 2}

@{_bullet}Send money in an envelope, together with the registration form.@{LIndent 2}

@{_bullet}Make an international postal money order, and send the registration form in an envelope.@{LIndent 2}

@{LIndent 0}@{Line}
You can choose whether to receive the keyfile via e-mail or via normal mail.@{LIndent 2}

@{_bullet}If you decide to receive it via e-mail, please specify your e-mail address on the registration form. This is the fastest and preferred method.@{LIndent 2}

@{_bullet}If you decide to receive it via normal mail, please enclose a pre-formatted floppy disk (Amiga DD 880k or MS-DOS DD 720k) into the envelope.@{LIndent 2}

@{LIndent 0}@{Line}
I will ship you the keyfile as soon as I have received BOTH the registration form AND the money. If you request a shipment via normal mail, please allow 2-8 weeks for delivery.@{par}

Send registration to:@{par}
@{jcenter}
@{"Ralph Torchia" link "Author"@}@{par}
5995 Ellis Unit 219@{par}
LaSalle, Ontario@{par}
CANADA  N9H 2P1@{par}
@{jleft}

If anything is not clear, please write to me for more information.@{par}

Thank you!@{par}

@endnode



