@{_Section "Demo Limitations"}

The unregistered demo version of Spitfireý has the following limitations:

@{_bullet}Requesters reminding the user to register their copy.@{LIndent 2}

@{_bullet}Maximum of 3 HotSync, without quiting and restarting the program.@{LIndent 2}

@{_bullet}Time limit of 20 minutes.@{LIndent 2}

